data.description: Very well thought out placement of storage, laundry room & closets in this desirable 55+ community!  Steps away from all of the conveniences of NE Philly with a SUBURBAN feel : ) Well maintained LARGE 3 bedroom with 2 full baths twin home.  The primary bedroom includes a bathroom and AMPLE closet space.  OPEN common area hosting your kitchen with TONS of cabinets, counter space & pantry!  Also a comfortable living room with FIREPLACE.  The Club House hosts activities, pool, tennis courts, bocce ball & FABULOUS grounds!  *** Showings require 24 notice & must be confirmed with the owner via landline/answering machine.  Thank you for your patience. ***
